[
  {
    "start": 1.199,
    "end": 5.68,
    "text": "Hello there.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 3.04,
    "end": 9.599,
    "text": "Today we're going to do some shadowing",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 5.68,
    "end": 13.519,
    "text": "practice. One of the most effective ways",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 9.599,
    "end": 16.64,
    "text": "to improve listening, fluency, and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 13.519,
    "end": 20.08,
    "text": "confidence. Remember,  you don't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 16.64,
    "end": 23.58,
    "text": "need to be perfect and you don't need to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 20.08,
    "end": 25.84,
    "text": "understand every single word. Just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 23.58,
    "end": 28.88,
    "text": " speak with me.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 25.84,
    "end": 31.84,
    "text": "In case you are new to shadowing,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 28.88,
    "end": 35.92,
    "text": "let me explain what shadowing is.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 31.84,
    "end": 38.8,
    "text": "Shadowing is a practice where you listen",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 35.92,
    "end": 43.2,
    "text": "to a native English speaker such as",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 38.8,
    "end": 48.399,
    "text": "myself and you repeat what I say at the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 43.2,
    "end": 49.44,
    "text": "same time as me. Make sure to copy",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 48.399,
    "end": 52.64,
    "text": "rhythm, ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 49.44,
    "end": 54.879,
    "text": "stress, and speed.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.64,
    "end": 58.0,
    "text": "Don't stop  for mistakes. It's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 54.879,
    "end": 63.039,
    "text": "okay. Just keep going.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 58.0,
    "end": 64.845,
    "text": "Now I'll say a natural short monologue.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 63.039,
    "end": 66.08,
    "text": "We will do it three times together.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 64.845,
    "end": 70.0,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 66.08,
    "end": 71.92,
    "text": "First at a normal speed, second in a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 70.0,
    "end": 76.159,
    "text": "slow speed,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 71.92,
    "end": 80.0,
    "text": "and third in a natural speed. Again,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 76.159,
    "end": 83.92,
    "text": "let's get started. First round, normal",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.0,
    "end": 86.32,
    "text": "speed. Lately, work's been pretty busy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 83.92,
    "end": 88.08,
    "text": "I've had a lot of meetings and it feels",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 86.32,
    "end": 91.52,
    "text": "like there's always something else to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 88.08,
    "end": 94.159,
    "text": "do. I'm trying not to stress too much",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 91.52,
    "end": 97.84,
    "text": "though and just take things one step at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 94.159,
    "end": 101.36,
    "text": "a time. All right, now you've listened.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 97.84,
    "end": 105.52,
    "text": "Let's try it together slowly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 101.36,
    "end": 108.32,
    "text": "Lately, work's been pretty busy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 105.52,
    "end": 110.799,
    "text": "I've had a lot of meetings",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.32,
    "end": 113.52,
    "text": "and it feels like there's always",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 110.799,
    "end": 116.32,
    "text": "something else  to do.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 113.52,
    "end": 120.719,
    "text": "I'm trying not to stress too much,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 116.32,
    "end": 123.92,
    "text": "though, and just  take things",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 120.719,
    "end": 128.0,
    "text": "one step at a time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 123.92,
    "end": 130.72,
    "text": "All right, time for natural speed again.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 128.0,
    "end": 133.84,
    "text": "This time, follow along.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 130.72,
    "end": 136.72,
    "text": "Lately, work's been pretty busy. I've",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 133.84,
    "end": 140.08,
    "text": "had a lot of meetings, and it feels like",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 136.72,
    "end": 142.879,
    "text": "there's always something else to do. I'm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 140.08,
    "end": 146.56,
    "text": "trying not to stress too much though and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 142.879,
    "end": 148.48,
    "text": "just take things one step at a time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 146.56,
    "end": 150.16,
    "text": "Did you do it?  Did you follow",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 148.48,
    "end": 154.56,
    "text": "along?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 150.16,
    "end": 158.08,
    "text": "Great job. You did so well. Now, a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 154.56,
    "end": 161.599,
    "text": "little bit of a bonus mini shadow.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 158.08,
    "end": 163.519,
    "text": "First, let's try just normal speed. This",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 161.599,
    "end": 166.48,
    "text": "weekend,  I'm planning to just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 163.519,
    "end": 168.8,
    "text": "take it easy. I don't really want to do",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 166.48,
    "end": 171.36,
    "text": "anything too busy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 168.8,
    "end": 175.541,
    "text": "I might meet a friend, catch up on some",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 171.36,
    "end": 178.48,
    "text": "rest, and just relax at home. All right,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 175.541,
    "end": 180.56,
    "text": " now a little slower. This",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 178.48,
    "end": 183.84,
    "text": "weekend,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 180.56,
    "end": 186.959,
    "text": "I'm planning to take it easy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 183.84,
    "end": 191.12,
    "text": "I don't really want to do anything too",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 186.959,
    "end": 194.0,
    "text": "busy. I might meet a friend,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 191.12,
    "end": 197.519,
    "text": "catch up on some rest,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 194.0,
    "end": 201.12,
    "text": "and just relax at home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 197.519,
    "end": 203.519,
    "text": "Now, back up to natural speed.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 201.12,
    "end": 206.72,
    "text": "This weekend, I'm planning to take it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 203.519,
    "end": 210.64,
    "text": "easy. I don't really want to do anything",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 206.72,
    "end": 216.799,
    "text": "too busy. I might meet a friend, catch",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 210.64,
    "end": 219.36,
    "text": "up on some rest, and just relax at home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 216.799,
    "end": 221.44,
    "text": "Excellent job.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 219.36,
    "end": 224.56,
    "text": "Now, if this is your first time",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 221.44,
    "end": 227.44,
    "text": "shadowing and it felt difficult,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 224.56,
    "end": 230.959,
    "text": "it's completely normal.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 227.44,
    "end": 233.519,
    "text": "Shadowing is not about perfect grammar",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 230.959,
    "end": 238.799,
    "text": "or perfect pronunciation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 233.519,
    "end": 241.36,
    "text": "It's about rhythm, flow, and confidence.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 238.799,
    "end": 245.04,
    "text": "If you want to improve your English",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 241.36,
    "end": 248.879,
    "text": "speaking ability and fluency and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 245.04,
    "end": 252.879,
    "text": "confidence, I recommend doing some short",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 248.879,
    "end": 255.439,
    "text": "five minute shadowing practices a day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 252.879,
    "end": 260.0,
    "text": "You can choose one short video like this",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 255.439,
    "end": 264.479,
    "text": "one and practice shadowing a paragraph",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 260.0,
    "end": 267.52,
    "text": "which is about four sentences long or so",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 264.479,
    "end": 269.04,
    "text": "and repeat what is being said without",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 267.52,
    "end": 270.96,
    "text": "stopping.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 269.04,
    "end": 273.84,
    "text": "This actually works better than studying",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 270.96,
    "end": 276.0,
    "text": "for hours and hours.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 273.84,
    "end": 278.16,
    "text": "Well, that concludes our shadowing",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 276.0,
    "end": 281.04,
    "text": "practice for this video. Hope that you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 278.16,
    "end": 282.639,
    "text": "enjoyed it and found it useful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 281.04,
    "end": 287.52,
    "text": "Remember,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 282.639,
    "end": 289.36,
    "text": "fluency comes from use, practice,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 287.52,
    "end": 291.52,
    "text": "not perfection.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 289.36,
    "end": 293.52,
    "text": "If you found this video helpful at all,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 291.52,
    "end": 295.68,
    "text": "I would really appreciate it if you like",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 293.52,
    "end": 298.72,
    "text": "the video and subscribed to  the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 295.68,
    "end": 301.52,
    "text": "channel. It really helps me to continue",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 298.72,
    "end": 305.12,
    "text": "what I'm doing. And that is hopefully",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 301.52,
    "end": 308.639,
    "text": "helping you to learn English and become",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 305.12,
    "end": 311.12,
    "text": "more fluent and confident. Okay, I'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 308.639,
    "end": 315.8,
    "text": "see you in the next video. Have a nice",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 311.12,
    "end": 315.8,
    "text": "day. Bye bye.",
    "textdich": ""
  }
]